      <textAnnotation id="sid-B6B7FCD6-2A2E-413F-83DB-E1F031F6E287" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower : OTC  Order to Cash
Process Group: O Order Management
Process: O-040-040A Maintain Promotion Tables (IP)

</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DD6ED8B6-F917-4FFD-8A82-C78B37A56D60" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1.Manual Upload takes place when the Boundary Apps are facing downtime.
2.Create, Change and expirations will be taking place
3.If a promotion is time bound, the promotion is introduced and expired based on entered dates.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
