         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform Process Steward:  Galceran, Nuria &lt;nuria.galceran@intel.com&gt;, and BPM Champion: Rebeca, Meza Redondo &lt;rebeca.meza.redondo@intel.com&gt; of any changes that occur within the flow from now onwards so that changes can be accurately reflected within BIC</text>
